jei.wallpapercraft.solidgray-0.desc:
The base WallpaperCraft crafting block.

Combine with one to three Presses to change its look.

Any WallpaperCraft block, not just the base block, can be altered this way.
jei.wallpapercraft.paintbrush.desc: Left-click on opaque (non-glass) blocks in-world to cycle through their colors.
